<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c4">[٥٠٦]</span> في <span class="c2">(أ)</span> ، <span class="c2">(ب)</span> : <span class="c2">(يقع الطلاق)</span> .<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
